ated at thank you page'=>'客户仍可购买门票，但会在 "感谢 "页面生成信息','The Default Raffle is the main raffle, and all other raffles created inherit some of the settings from it'=>'默认抽奖活动是主要的抽奖活动，所有其他创建的抽奖活动都继承了它的一些设置。','The keywords will be replaced with the numbers when displayed'=>'显示时，关键字将被数字取代','The plugin is not licensed'=>'该插件未获许可','The Plugin requires no special installation, just as any regular plugin proceed with instalation, and activation.'=>'该插件不需要特别的安装，就像任何普通的插件一样，要进行安装和激活。','The Progress bar does not show in the position you have selected? Some themes change the position of hooks with different style or html applied to the page.'=>'进度条没有显示在您选择的位置上？有些主题会根据页面应用的不同样式或 HTML 更改钩子的位置。','The Raffle does not generate tickets randomly - Change to random generated'=>'抽奖券不是随机生成的 - 改为随机生成','The Raffle does not have limited tickets - Put a limit'=>'抽奖券不设上限 - 设置上限','The raffle has limited tickets - notify user - eg: 3 tickets left, user wants to buy 5, exceeds with 2 - show message'=>'抽奖活动的票数有限--通知用户--例如：剩下3张票，用户想买5张，超出2张--显示信息','The raffle has limited tickets - Upon adding to cart, the system checks if any tickets left, if not show message '=>'抽奖活动的门票有限 - 加入购物车后，系统会检查是否有剩余的门票，如果没有，则显示消息','The raffle is set as terminated'=>'抽奖活动被设定为终止','The raffle will be set to terminated if the "Buyout Product" is out of stock.'=>'如果 "买断产品 "缺货，抽奖活动将被设定为终止。','The raffle will be set to terminated if the "Buyout Product" is sold (out of stock). Terminate Raffle by selling a single not raffle product.'=>'如果 "买断产品 "被售出（缺货），抽奖活动将被设置为终止。通过出售单一的非抽奖产品来终止抽奖活动。','The raffle will be terminated. No raffle tickets will be available for sale.'=>'抽奖活动将被终止。没有抽奖券可供出售。','The raffle will have a limited number of tickets'=>'抽奖活动的门票数量有限','The system will do it automatically based on the rules'=>'系统会根据规则自动执行','The tickets will be generated and shown at checkout page'=>'门票将在结账页面生成并显示','There are issues with the DB Tables'=>'DB表有问题','There is a custom reserved time in minutes'=>'自定义预留时间，单位为分钟','These labels will show in the \'Thank you page\' and the \'Confirmation Email\' '=>'这些标签将显示在 "感谢页面 "和 "确认电子邮件 "中。','These tickets are counted as purchased because are reserved for the customer for a specific time'=>'这些门票被算作已购票，因为它们是在特定时间内为客户预留的','This is a promotional raffle, based on your cart value we award free entry tickets to raffle.'=>'这是一次促销抽奖活动，我们将根据您的购物车价值发放免费抽奖券。','This is a won ticket, are you sure?'=>'这是一张中奖彩票，你确定吗？','This is the minimal setup to have a raffle running'=>'这是进行抽奖活动的最基本设置','This page is set only to keep track of the winning tickets, and the customers associated'=>'这个页面的设置只是为了跟踪中奖彩票，以及与之相关的客户。','Ticket'=>'票务','Ticket Changed Successfully'=>'机票已成功更改','Ticket From'=>'票价从','Ticket Height'=>'门票高度','Ticket Info Position'=>'门票信息位置','Ticket Number'=>'票号','Ticket Number does not exist'=>'票号不存在','Ticket Number Leading Zeros'=>'票号前导零','Ticket Prefix'=>'票据前缀','Ticket To'=>'票价','Ticket Width'=>'票宽','Ticket-'=>'票务-','Tickets are generated and displayed per raffle, you need to enable the option for each raffle'=>'每次抽奖都会生成和显示门票，您需要为每次抽奖启用该选项','Tickets can now be generated and displayed at checkout before the order is placed'=>'现在可在下订单前生成并在结账时显示票据','Tickets Info'=>'门票信息','Tickets Purchased'=>'购买的门票','Tickets will not be visible at checkout anymore'=>'结账时将不再显示门票','Tickets will only be generated for these order statuses'=>'只有这些订单状态才会生成订单','To'=>'拟','to display link to product (Thank you page / Email)'=>'显示产品链接（感谢页面/电子邮件）','To display messages in custom page, copy the shortcode, change the it to match the raffle id and paste it in custom page'=>'要在自定义页面中显示消息，请复制简码，将其更改为与抽奖 ID 匹配，然后将其粘贴到自定义页面中','To display the raffle name add show_raffle_name in the shortcode'=>'为了显示抽奖活动的名称，在短码中添加show_raffle_name。','To show raffle name add (show_raffle_name=\'1\') in the shortcode'=>'为了显示抽奖活动的名称，在短码中添加(show_raffle_name=\'1\')','Top of Single Product Summary'=>'单个产品摘要顶部','Total'=>'共计','Total Tickets'=>'总票数','Two'=>'二','Two customers buying raffle products at the same time, might cause the db to overlap the orders, and create duplicate tickets. Chances are minimal. But the system will spot any malfunctions '=>'两个客户同时购买抽奖产品，可能会导致数据库中的订单重叠，并产生重复的彩票。机会是最小的。但系统会发现任何故障','Under \'Product\' page go to \'General\' tab and you should see two extra options '=>'在 "产品 "页面下，进入 "常规 "标签，你应该看到两个额外的选项','Unique identifier for the shortcode'=>'简码的唯一标识符','unlimited'=>'无限','Up to 1000 random numbers displayed. Want more? Use filter '=>'最多可显示 1000 个随机数字。想要更多？使用过滤器','up to 1000 random tickets will be displayed, can be increased, use filter '=>'最多显示 1000 张随机门票，可以增加，使用过滤器','Update / Delete / Add to Cart Promotional Product message'=>'更新/删除/添加到购物车 促销产品信息','Update Cart (exceeding tickets %d)'=>'更新购物车（超过票数%d）。','Update Cart (limit on - exceeding tickets - %d)'=>'更新购物车（限制 - 超过票数 - %d)','Updated - Compatible with new HPOS, and legacy order storage '=>'更新 - 与新的 HPOS 和传统订单存储兼容','Url redirect when clicking on image (like url to product)'=>'点击图片时重定向网址（如产品网址）','Use'=>'使用','Use spaces as delimiter'=>'使用空格作为分隔符','Use Variation Product Raffle'=>'使用变化 产品抽奖','Used with \'Test\' option in the settings'=>'与设置中的 "测试 "选项一起使用','Used with ticket number as Tkt-1001, Tkt-1002, etc. Instead of display a dull number as 1001, 1002'=>'与Tkt-1001, Tkt-1002等票号一起使用。而不是显示一个枯燥的数字，如1001，1002','User Message are very effective on showing the tickets status to the users'=>'用户信息在向用户显示票据状态方面非常有效。','User Messages'=>'用户信息','Validate License'=>'验证许可证','Value Above'=>'以上价值','Variable'=>'可变','Version'=>'版本','Very IMPORTANT to setup messages'=>'设置信息非常重要','Video available'=>'提供视频','View'=>'查看','View more here'=>'在此查看更多信息','View PDF'=>'查看 PDF','View PDF Attachment Documentation '=>'查看 PDF 附件文档 %s','View Positions %s'=>'查看职位 %s','View Tickets'=>'查看门票','View Tickets by Order'=>'按订单查看门票','View your sale by raffle'=>'通过抽奖查看您的销售情况','wait to load after changing status'=>'改变状态后等待加载','Warning. There is another column with same DB Meta Name'=>'警告。有另一列具有相同的DB元名称','Watch explanation %s and %s on this youtube videos I made'=>'在我制作的这段 youtube 视频中观看解释 %s','Watch promotional raffle setup video here'=>'点击此处观看抽奖设置宣传视频','Watch setup video'=>'观看设置视频','Watch setup video here'=>'点击此处观看安装视频','Watch the video on the right for better understanding.'=>'请观看右侧的视频，以便更好地理解。','Watch video before proceding. How to promote shop with free raffle'=>'开始前请观看视频。如何通过免费抽奖推广店铺','Week'=>'周','Weekly Sales'=>'每周销售','What is HPOS? Read more about it here'=>'什么是 HPOS？点击此处了解更多','When printing if the background image is not visible, go to print page -> More Settings and select "Background graphics" from the options.'=>'打印时，如果背景图片不可见，请进入打印页面 -> 更多设置，然后从选项中选择 "背景图形"。','While running a raffle reward your customers with smaller prizes as instant wins'=>'在进行抽奖活动时，将较小的奖品作为即时奖品回馈客户','Why Duplicates? Slow hosting, too many order requests at the same time (server cannot cope), caching issues.'=>'为什么会出现重复订单？主机速度慢、同时有太多订单请求（服务器无法处理）、缓存问题。','Winner'=>'冠军','Winners'=>'获奖者','Winning Message'=>'获奖感言','With this shortcode you can retrieve the primary attributes of any raffle. 
                                                            It can be used to display raffle information or integrate it with other plugins. Check the link below to the youtube video.'=>'使用此简码，您可以检索任何抽奖活动的主要属性。
                                                            它可用于显示抽奖信息或与其他插件集成。请查看下面的 youtube 视频链接。','Won'=>'获胜','Won Ticket'=>'旧票','Woocommerce Account'=>'Woocommerce 账户','Woocommerce has made changes to cart and checkout pages recently.'=>'Woocommerce 最近对购物车和结账页面进行了修改。','Woocommerce Info'=>'Woocommerce 信息','Works only with PHP version 7.1, and above'=>'仅在PHP7.1及以上版本中工作','Yes'=>'是','You can define a winning number or let the system pick one. It only works with Random Tickets'=>'您可以定义一个中奖号码，也可以让系统选择一个中奖号码。它只适用于随机彩票','You can place custom progress bar on any page with the following shortcode - if options left empty will pick the default setting set above.'=>'您可以使用以下简码在任何页面上放置自定义进度条--如果选项留空，将使用上述默认设置。','You dont have access'=>'您没有访问权限','Your license is not valid'=>'你的驾照是无效的','Your PHP version is less than 7.1, therefore this feature wont work'=>'你的PHP版本小于7.1，因此该功能不能工作。','Your server\'s PHP version: '=>'你的服务器的PHP版本。']];
